m nhật tác kỳ 1 - 在金日作其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-V%C4%83n-H%C6%B0-Trung/author-d591GXqfH9P8L_1V1LEy2A">Vũ Văn Hư Trung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-L%E1%BB%87nh/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Th%E1%BA%ADn-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-M%E1%BB%B9-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A2n/poem-XVA4cNPxsOFLLCYScuZlYA">Tặng Thận Đông Mỹ Bá Quân - 赠慎東美伯筠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-L%E1%BB%87nh/author-Wi4-g6g_EJiYCavfRigKbw">Vương Lệnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-xfUL0RFU1M6WV9XOi__Sxg">Thiên vấn - 天問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Th%E1%BB%A5c-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-nan/poem-vwkwYNzCnKHaayHMN3KvlQ">Thục đạo nan - 蜀道難</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Ti%E1%BB%83u-nhung-1/poem-cLbuuwhe3xqD03aZlR-Yjw">Tiểu nhung 1 - 小戎 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
